textAfterTable: 13 Songs Customer Reviews Love it           by Christiana It came as no surprise to me that I liked this album because I have been a fan of the band for a while now, loving both of their previous CDs. I liked this album because it had some slower songs and a couple heavier ones too keeping people on both sides of the spectrum satisfied. I can't even pick a favorite song but a couple I really liked were "Behind Those Eyes", "My World", and "Live for Today". Also "Right Where I Belong" is an awesome opening song-- it rocks!!
